#: ../../../admin-guide/ext4.rst:172
msgid "data=journal"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/ext4.rst:173
msgid ""
"All data are committed into the journal prior to being written into the main "
"file system.  Enabling this mode will disable delayed allocation and "
