"blocks allocated out of a block group specific preallocation pool, so that "
"small files are packed closely together.  Each large file will have its "
"blocks allocated out of its own unique preallocation pool."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/ext4.rst:505
msgid "session_write_kbytes"
